<action> must be one of the following:

    config                           Generate a config/captcha.yml file.
    
    image_directory                  Create a directory for storing generated
                                     images. Will use the value of 'default_dir'
                                     from config/captcha.yml if it exists.
    
    store_directory                  Create a directory for storing CAPTCHA objects.
                                     Will use the value of 'store' from
                                     config/captcha.yml if it exists.

